We love a good kitchen renovation! The new kitchen in this @dvharchitects Classic Georgian Restoration project pays homage to the original era of the house while seamlessly integrating modern appliances and storage solutions. It features a custom farm table, restored range hood and farm sink. Swipe to see the space before its transformation.⁣
